OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mixed day of
OL,6,Fbright and sunny spells with a few
OL,7,Fshowers possible. Showers may be heavy
OL,8,Fand perhaps thundery at times. Fresh
OL,9,Fwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome late bright or sunny
OL,12,Fspells this evening but heavy and
OL,13,Fperhaps thundery showers around.
OL,14,FOvernight will see showers gradually
OL,15,Fease with some clear intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
