OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA largely dry day with
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells, possibly a
OL,7,Flight, isolated shower in the morning.
OL,8,FCloud and rain spreading
OL,9,Fnortheastwards in the evening. Fresh
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds turning southerly.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLow
OL,13,Fcloud and rain Friday clears to the
OL,14,Fnorth to leave bright spells and
OL,15,Fshowers. Bright spells and showers
OL,16,FSaturday. Dry with sunny periods
OL,17,FSunday. Stronger winds Friday then
OL,18,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
